twcore.bots.multibot.baseassault
Class baseassault

java.lang.Object
  twcore.bots.MultiModule
      twcore.bots.multibot.baseassault.baseassault

public class baseassault
extends MultiModule

TWBot Extension for use in basing maps. Lagouts and late adds will be possible. Consists of two teams. One team will begin the match with the base in their possession. The other team will try to capture the flag as quickly as possible. Once the seconds team succeeds, the two teams swap positions. Two game modes will exist: a) The team with the fastest time wins. b) the game will continue until a time has not been beat.

Version:
0.89
Author:
script
